{"prompt": "Produce a platform for a virtual reality experience developer. The design should be immersive, with an electric yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>VR Experience Developer</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #111;\n            color: #eee;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            height: 100vh;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511107976240-c088f50963d1?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80');\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #ffff00; /* Electric Yellow */\n            text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffff00, 0 0 25px #ffff00;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            background-color: #ffff00; /* Electric Yellow */\n            color: #111;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ffff00;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0e000;\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n        .section {\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #ffff00;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ffff00;\n        }\n        .features {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 300px;\n            margin: 20px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.1); /* Subtle yellow tint */\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ffff00;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            color: #ffff00;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .contact {\n            background-color: #222;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n        }\n        .contact h2 {\n            color: #eee;\n            text-shadow: none;\n        }\n        .contact p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ffff00;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #111;\n            color: #eee;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            background-color: #ffff00;\n            color: #111;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0e000;\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #111;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            border-top: 1px solid #ffff00;\n        }\n        .pulsing-circle {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.3);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        .pulsing-circle::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out reverse;\n        }\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }\n            50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.5); opacity: 0.2; }\n            100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .section h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .features {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n            .feature-item {\n                width: 80%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"pulsing-circle\"></div>\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h1>Immerse Yourself</h1>\n            <p>Crafting breathtaking virtual realities that transport your users to new dimensions. Let's build the future, together.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Start Your Project</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Our Expertise</h2>\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Unrivaled Realism</h3>\n                <p>Leveraging cutting-edge technology to create experiences so real, you'll forget it's virtual.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Interactive Storytelling</h3>\n                <p>We don't just build worlds, we craft narratives that captivate and engage.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Seamless Integration</h3>\n                <p>From concept to deployment, we ensure a smooth and efficient development process.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section contact\">\n        <h2>Let's Connect</h2>\n        <p>Ready to bring your VR vision to life? Get in touch with our team.</p>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\">\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Tell us about your project...\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 VR Experience Developer. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic parallax effect for the hero background\n        const hero = document.querySelector('.hero');\n        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {\n            const scrollPosition = window.pageYOffset;\n            hero.style.backgroundPositionY = `${scrollPosition * 0.5}px`;\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}